# Web-only devshell — Node 22 + pnpm, no Rust toolchain.
# Overrides the parent `.envrc` when you `cd web`.
#
# Reads the ROOT flake (../flake.nix). No per-subdirectory flake
# exists — kobu has exactly one source of truth at the repo root.
# `watch_file` makes direnv reload this shell whenever the root
# flake or its lockfile changes, so bumping Node at the root
# invalidates the web cache too.
watch_file ../flake.nix ../flake.lock
use flake "path:..#web"
